@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_eqgrgs(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = v2
    v0 = wp.abs(v2)
    v2 = (wp.sin(wp.exp(v1 + 0.07)) / ((tmp + 0.01 / tmp + 0.19) - tmp))
    v1 = (tmp + wp.exp((v0 + 0.45 / v1 + 0.66)))
    tmp = (0.69 + (wp.cos(tmp + 0.44) * 0.65))
    v0 = (v0 - (tmp / (v1 + 0.84 / v2 + 0.09)))
    v0 = wp.abs(0.08)
    v0 = (v0 + 0.39)
    data[tid] = v0
